{"tid":452552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨成功爭取 西洋菜街大媽於何文田登台獻唱表演！","createTime":"2017-10-30T10:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T10:50:40.000Z","uid":107941,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b659caffd38d78be6b38abe4821870c6d4d2f9b","tid":452552,"uid":107941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/182625_dd563a7d21fc37316e37c6b963d9637e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F182625_dd563a7d21fc37316e37c6b963d9637e.jpg&h=33a31ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使出旺角都可以欣賞到菜街大媽嘅嘔心表演同嘈音啦屌你老母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黃碧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陳麗君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 菜街大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查過下係慈善演唱會黎，邊個負責場show邊個負責請嘉賓係唔清楚嘅。如果有該區居民影到宣傳海報可能有多啲資料。<br />\n但咁撚大支旗咁撚大個名，唔多謝民主黨多謝邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望好快喺其他屋邨，民主黨都可以爭取到班大媽黎表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb4639251388614bec992c8f66dcc6a6a78319a","tid":452552,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c420f7848afc425373581afe556cfca62beaf4","tid":452552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"夠弱智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}